dition of contract for the supply of stores and materials to the Military Engineer Services (IAFW – 1815–Z) General Condition of contract for Measurement contract (IAFW-2249) Participants must be Enlisted with MES Under HQ CE EC/ HQ CWE Kolkata and the Products are being used must be Approved in CMPT list of HQ CE EC. GeM Star rating of Firm must be greater than or equal to 4.0 The above terms and conditions are in reverse order of precedence i.e. ATC shall supersede Se rvice specific STC which shall supersede GTC, in case of any conflicting provisions. This document represents a Special Terms and Conditions (“STC”) the Service Level Agreement (SLA) gove rning the contract between the Buyer and Service Provider. The purpose of this document is to outline the scope of work, Stakeholder’s obligation and terms and conditions of all services covered as mutually under stood by the stakeholders. Payment Terms • The Payment shall be made on completion of service or monthly basis. . 8 / 10

